OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784888303
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years for murder of
OL,4,Cteenage boy on e-bike
OL,6,FA man who killed a teenage boy on an e-
OL,7,Fbike after ramming him with his car
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for 17 years.
OL,10,FTerrence King, 60, was found guilty of
OL,11,Fkilling Devon Simmonds-Caines after
OL,12,Fdeliberately driving his car into him
OL,13,Fon Rowrah Crescent in Middleton,
OL,14,FManchester.
OL,16,FKing had been chasing the e-bike,
OL,17,Fwhich had been reportedly stolen,
OL,18,Fsteering his vehicle directly at the
OL,19,Fteenager at speed without braking, on
OL,20,F22 July 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
