PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784888303
OL,3,CMan jailed for 17 years for murder of
OL,4,Cteenage boy on e-bike
OL,6,FEmergency services immediately
OL,7,Fattended but despite their best
OL,8,Fefforts, Devon, aged 15, was died at
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FKing was found guilty of murder at
OL,12,FManchester Crown Court on 17 July.
OL,14,FFollowing his death, Devon's family
OL,15,Freleased a tribute, calling him a
OL,16,F"bubbly person" who "only wanted the
OL,17,Fbest for everyone around him".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
